name: Younow - Dark
description: Just made it dark real quick. nothing special
css:
@-moz-document domain("www.younow.com") {
body{
	background: #333333;
}

#player-toolbar,
.navbar-content .search-box .search-field,
.navbar-content .notifications .search-field,
#playerheader,
#sidebar-container,
#sidebar-container #chatcomments
{
	background-color: #444;
}

body,
#sidebar-container #chatcomments .chat-name, 
#sidebar-container #chatcomments .ynicon-level,
#playerheader .broadcaster-name, 
#playerheader .broadcaster-name span, 
#playerheader .broadcaster-tags, 
#playerheader .broadcaster-setup-description,
.player-toolbar-left .ynicon,
#player-toolbar-right span,
#player-toolbar-right .volume-icon,
.toolbar-like-count, 
.share-like-count,
#sidebar-container #topfan-slider
{
	color: #568B08;
}

#sidebar-container #chatcomments span,
#leftsidebar .trending-tag, 
#leftsidebar .trending-user, 
#leftsidebar .viewerCount,
#playerheader .broadcaster-description,
#leftsidebar .trending-tag, 
#leftsidebar .trending-user, 
#leftsidebar .viewerCount,
span,
.navbar-content .explore-text a, 
.navbar-content .login-text a,
.navbar-content .search-box .search-field, 
.navbar-content .notifications .search-field,
#sidebar-container #chatcomments span
{
	color: #FFF;
}
}
